title: Add HeightMapProfiler.
message:
Add HeightMapProfiler.

This is a simple application for benchmarking 3D performance of Android handsets.  It generates a height map-based landscape and allows the user to tweak OpenGL ES state and scene complexity to see how various Android devices perform.  When the test is complete, profiling results (including average verts per frame and total frame time) are reported.

title: Fix SpriteMethodTest to use direct buffers for VBOs.  Indirect buffers are…
message:
Fix SpriteMethodTest to use direct buffers for VBOs.  Indirect buffers are problematic for two reasons: they violate the OpenGL ES spec, and they can cause incorrect drawing (or even a crash) if the GC moves buffer memory around without GL being told about it.  Under Donus use of indirect buffers with glXXXPointer() functions will throw an exceptions, but earlier versions of the SDK do not.

title: Interim commit of import/export functionality for WikiNotes.
message:
Interim commit of import/export functionality for WikiNotes.

Currently import and export to XML via SD card works.  There are two known bugs
that I want to fix before cutting a release for Market:
1. Import needs to cause the Activity currently displayed to reload so that it
   doesn't show old data.
2. Documentation is currently poor.

This change also adds a EULA-style help menu that gives some basic usage info
as well as "about the authors/app" stuff.

I wouldn't normally commit this change in this state but I don't trust this
laptop and don't want to lose my work. :)
